Collectible Wedding Trio Gift Set
List.Description:
To have and to hold, to sip and to savor. If you're looking for the perfect wedding gift for the wine-loving couple, look no further. Our Collectible Wedding Trio celebrates the newlyweds by giving them bottles to have AND to hold. Hold onto that is. In this gift, which we like to call the 1-5-10, we feature three wines: One to toast the first wedding anniversary, one to enjoy fifth anniversary and one to celebrate the tenth anniversary. Comes with our signature wedding greet sheet as pictured.

Gift includes a bottle of each:

  • FIRST ANNIVERSARY:
    Bollinger Special Cuvée Champagne
    A classic Champagne that will sparkle as bright as her diamond. Bollinger is known for its full body and rich texture, as well as Madame Lily Bollinger, who ran the house during World War II and beyond. She loved her country and her Champagne with a passion that you can taste in the Champagne today.

  • FIFTH ANNIVERSARY:
    Chimney Rock Stag's Leap Cabernet Sauvignon
    This is a classic California Cabernet Sauvignon, ideal for laying down a few years. From the unique and renowned Stag's Leap District of Napa Valley, Chimney Rock set out to make wines on par with the classic wines of Bordeaux. Their Cabernet Sauvignons are elegant and structured and perfect for a celebratory event.

  • TENTH ANNIVERSARY:
    Il Poggione Brunello di Montalcino
    This wine needs a decade to show what it can do. The Il Poggione Brunello di Montalcino will evolve beautifully and make that 10th anniversary night one to remember. This winery has been making wine in Tuscany for over a century, and they have perfected the art of making wines that receive widespread critical acclaim.

Due to the popularity of this gift, wines or vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage and wines with equal or greater value.

Schott Zwiesel Cru Classic - Set of 6 Red Wine Glasses
List.Description:
German glass-maker Schott Zwiesel boasts a 130-year-history of innovation and success, including such break-throughs as the first machine-made stemware and the first lead-free crystal glass. They‚Äôve once again revolutionized the industry, with the introduction Tritan Crystal glassware, which is made with titanium and zirconium instead of lead. Rigorous laboratory testing has proven the brilliance, dishwasher safety, and break-resistance of Tritan. These glasses are not only break-, scratch- and chip- resistant, but also beautiful.

Delicately shaped to open the wine and deliver its full taste, the Schott Zwiesel Cru Classic line has fully rounded bowls and graceful stems to beautifully accent the table setting.

The Schott Zwiesel Cru Classis Red Wine glasses are meant for light reds.

Made in Germany. Dishwasher safe. Each glass stands 8.7in and holds 19.8oz. Boxed set of 6.
